{"tid":1582471,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國朋友有啲嘢想同大家講","createTime":"2019-09-20T05:28:35.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T06:20:04.000Z","uid":63864,"like":7,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"90f4d95e4c6af13f361bbff8d08f890517ecc425","tid":1582471,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:28:35.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\">代Post</span><br />\n<br />\n利申：有去發夢但冇行到好前，見過火魔法師喺我面前施法，當刻不明所以，不過本住 <span style=\"color: red;\">不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰</span> 嘅原則，我做見證人算。<br />\n<br />\n美國朋友一直都好關心香港時局，繼上次搞咗個Popo攝影比賽，今次佢又有啲嘢想講，唔想睇英文可以淨係睇下面幾行，再碌落啲有原文。<br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n1. 建議大家唔好施魔法住，留個好印象畀美國民眾。<br />\n2. 大肆宣揚我哋唔會擲嘢，到時有人擲大家就識質疑，唔會賴火魔法師<br />\n3. 唔係想打擊士氣，淨係想減低法案唔過嘅風險<br />\n4. 想畀多個方向手足諗吓</span><br />\n<br />\n//<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">原文：<br />\nI have been thinking of something... even if the congress and senate pass the law, it is up to the government execute the law or what not. Here are my thought...<br />\n<br />\nIf protesters kept using violence act such as throwing Molotov cocktail bombs or beating up the pro-government protesters, it might be hard for US government to execute the law due to fact that both sides are violence. A lot of American don&rsquo;t understand why those protesters set up fire or whatsoever. It might be good to stop using fire or throwing Molotov cocktail. Protesters or LIHK now should condemn about using Molotov cocktail bomb or setting up fire. It will make it clear to the world those bombs are not from protesters. <br />\n<br />\nI am not trying to discourage the act, but we must not let the others have excuses to talk to the US government not to execute the law. <br />\n<br />\nIf you think my thought is reasonable, you should post it on LIHK and see how they feel about it.<br />\n<br />\nBe water, be smart and don&rsquo;t get arrested. Just hit and run and it works much better <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n最後，<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n我哋會贏！</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4addbe06b84645689b35ea5714c55bf8d492469c","tid":1582471,"uid":321501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:29:04.000Z","msg":"《If we burn, you burn with us》新歌出爐！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1581524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1581524</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"f09cfac32ca521c6c754aa1bdefcc6a22a66ed38","tid":1582471,"uid":321501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a79bffe134f28b3771ddf45a14a96843ea6d03c1","tid":1582471,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f09cfac32ca521c6c754aa1bdefcc6a22a66ed38","tid":1582471,"uid":321501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"p牌推唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:32:01.000Z","msg":"我唔記得出十連推！<br />\n10"},{"pid":"a04b6cf37cf7061c405182c2f9ca87b8e1be3121","tid":1582471,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:32:12.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"caf4eb239fe79e348216996149a7b4c03ddf0fc9","tid":1582471,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:32:23.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"d9792cd036cd58327c3fe79c65a47c4ea74ea6b9","tid":1582471,"uid":63864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:32:43.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"88eda2fe67b5d929810776a984d6dfddf7d5bc24","tid":1582471,"uid":18596,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T05:32:49.000Z","msg":"幫推<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":